{"tid":1436133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下每日四點笑黑警ErErEr緊要啲，定係推行動文宣策略Post緊要啲？","createTime":"2019-08-09T08:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T13:37:07.000Z","uid":36592,"like":120,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"466b9009ee213591e5603979e54eec849156e1e1","tid":1436133,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:28:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢條問題，大家自己答已經為呢場運動犧牲既烈士，被捕流亡受傷既義士，同埋每一位過去兩個月不顧一切全力付出既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>五大訴求，缺一不可</ins></span></strong><br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"329a683e06cbb0f16ac617ad78b5ef74ab757329","tid":1436133,"uid":153722,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依幾日好多垃圾分化 扯開話題既post<br />\n仆佢個街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家講反正經野<br />\n唔好比p牌三毛垃圾post阻撚住連登運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f2c3a0a6e12658a2b045b909daf123c9d3255b","tid":1436133,"uid":36592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:29:47.000Z","msg":"大家係咪想贏？係既請諗下應該將注意力擺喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31bdf56a49c6cb8ebe0f2ebe9b23c51a0e93d2e","tid":1436133,"uid":74958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:29:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3061bcb6654fc7622327c28a724779b1a67dd4e7","tid":1436133,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"